data.description: Move-In-Ready!   Charming and eclectic Farmhouse, Walk to Metro,  updates include EV charging station, new roof and gutters installed 2023,  one new A/C  2023, new carpet 2023, updated primary bathroom 2020, updated hall bathroom 2018, Bosch dishwasher and refrigerator 2020.  Ideally located within walking distance to Metro, schools, playgrounds, and a short distance to shopping and restaurants. This home features three levels of living with five bedrooms and four full bathrooms, a detached two car garage with attached garden shed built on an oversized lot of 14,790 Sq Ft.  This home has been freshly painted inside and out, includes hardwood floors on two levels, stainless steel appliances, granite surfaces and features many recent updates.  The main level consists of a formal living room with wood burning fireplace, formal sitting, and dining rooms a cozy office, a spacious family room, kitchen with breakfast bar, laundry room and a full bathroom.
